{
  "stem": "4570.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And if they didn't do something very bad, they obviously were not threatened or in danger.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We did not know about Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did not know about Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We did not know about anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All we knew that the Jews are going to be settled in, in like a ghetto-like place, Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Which didn't seem-- it seemed bad, of course, but it didn't seem that bad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody knew about Poland at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the eighth visit, somebody-- again, one of those girls-- came to me and said they changed, because somehow they didn't want to use the [?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bauhoff ?] anymore-- maybe there was some trouble-- and that Goldie had made contact with a Czech family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very charming, and his Czech was very good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and so he made contact with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked them if they would permit that I meet him there, and they said, yes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got the address of one of those little house and the time when I'm supposed to be there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was to bring money, and if-- probably salami, and nougat, and some other more essential things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So again, I, I had the two zipper bags.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I went-- I went to Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went into the hotel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when the time came, which was again, at night, I went, and I knocked there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The people opened and told that Goldie is upstairs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a little two0story house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, we exchanged-- you know, talking about the most important things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I gave him all, all, all what I brought.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
